name: Fox Earrings
description:
Fox face stud earring are made of shrinky dinks and attached to nickel earring posts with butterfly clutch backings to secure them when worn. When you purchase a pair of these earrings, they will be packaged in a little reusable box to store your earrings in and to protect them during shipping. 

Each pair of fox faces are matched up to make a symmetrical pair. The foxes are individually illustrated to look the same but will have slight differences.

measurements: 1cm x 1cm

Listing is for one pair of earrings.

Original illustration
© Leikey Designs 2011

name: Fox Brooch
description:
This little guy is hand embroidered on natural cotton muslin with cotton embroidery floss and stuffed with hand processed sheep's wool. 
Attach him to your favourite jacket, bag, blouse or shirt with the pin backing to add that little bit of sly style to your look. 

Approx, size: 2.5cm x 2cm

Listing is for one fox brooch

Original design
© Leikey Designs 2011

name: Fox Knot
description:
This cute little fox ring is hand felted with an embedded wire structure so you can easily adjust it to fit on your finger. 

Approx. measurements: height - to the tip of the ears is 3cm, band .5cm thick and head is 1cm wide

Listing is for one fox ring.
